snippet.title: Murder Cases - First Trailer
snippet.description:
Hello everybody!
I'm happy to announce the first trailer for one of our escape games still in development.

Murder Cases will be an escape room game with a mysterious theme, puzzles to solve, and comic-style visuals.

Song by cynicmusic
